PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID, RXMENUACTION.NAME, RXMENUACTION.URL, RXMENUACTION.URL AS url1 , RXMODE.MODEID, RXUICONTEXT.UICONTEXTID, RXMENUACTION.NAME AS name1 , RXMENUACTION.DISPLAYNAME, RXMENUACTION.SORTORDER, RXMENUACTION.TYPE, RXMENUACTION.HANDLER FROM RXMODE, RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION, RXUICONTEXT, RXMENUACTION WHERE RXMODE.MODEID = RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION.MODEID AND RXUICONTEXT.UICONTEXTID = RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION.UICONTEXTID AND RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID = RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION.ACTIONID AND RXMODE.NAME = ':"PSXSingleParam/sys_mode"' AND RXUICONTEXT.NAME = ':"PSXSingleParam/sys_uicontext"' AND RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID not in(select CHILDACTIONID from RXMENUACTIONRELATION) ORDER BY RXMENUACTION.SORTORDER ASC

SELECT RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID, RXMENUACTION.NAME, RXMENUACTION.URL, RXMENUACTION.URL AS url1 , RXMODE.MODEID, RXUICONTEXT.UICONTEXTID, RXMENUACTION.NAME AS name1 , RXMENUACTION.DISPLAYNAME, RXMENUACTION.SORTORDER, RXMENUACTION.TYPE, RXMENUACTION.HANDLER FROM RXMODE, RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION, RXUICONTEXT, RXMENUACTION WHERE RXMODE.MODEID = RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION.MODEID AND RXUICONTEXT.UICONTEXTID = RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION.UICONTEXTID AND RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID = RXMODEUICONTEXTACTION.ACTIONID AND RXMODE.NAME = ':"PSXSingleParam/sys_mode"' AND RXUICONTEXT.NAME = ':"PSXSingleParam/sys_uicontext"' AND RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID not in(select CHILDACTIONID from RXMENUACTIONRELATION) ORDER BY RXMENUACTION.SORTORDER ASC

SELECT DISTINCT RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID, RXMENUACTION.NAME, RXMENUACTION.SORTORDER FROM RXMODE, RXUICONTEXT, RXUICONTEXTACTION, RXMENUACTION, RXMENUACTIONRELATION WHERE RXMODE.MODEID = RXUICONTEXT.MODEID AND RXUICONTEXT.UICONTEXTID = RXUICONTEXTACTION.UICONTEXTID AND RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID = RXUICONTEXTACTION.ACTIONID AND RXMODE.NAME = ':"PSXSingleParam/sys_mode"' AND RXUICONTEXT.NAME = ':"PSXSingleParam/sys_uicontext"' AND RXMENUACTION.ACTIONID != RXMENUACTIONRELATION.ACTIONID ORDER BY RXMENUACTION.SORTORDER ASC

select DISTINCT PSX_SEARCHES.SEARCHID, PSX_SEARCHES.INTERNALNAME, PSX_SEARCHES.DISPLAYFORMAT, PSX_SEARCHES.DISPLAYNAME, PSX_SEARCHES.CUSTOMURL, PSX_SEARCHES.TYPE from PSX_SEARCHES, PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES where PSX_SEARCHES.PARENTCATEGORY = :"PSXSingleParam/sys_category" and PSX_SEARCHES.TYPE = 'View' and PSX_SEARCHES.SEARCHID = PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES.PROPERTYID and PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES.PROPERTYNAME = 'sys_community' and PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES.PROPERTYVALUE in ( '-1', ':"PSXUserContext/User/SessionObject/sys_community"') ORDER BY PSX_SEARCHES.DISPLAYNAME ASC

SELECT DISTINCT PSX_TEMPLATE.STYLESHEETNAME, PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID, PSX_TEMPLATE.ASSEMBLYURL, PSX_TEMPLATE.LABEL, PSX_TEMPLATE.OUTPUTFORMAT, PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME FROM PSX_TEMPLATE, RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE, CONTENTSTATUS, PSX_CONTENTTYPE_TEMPLATE CTT WHERE CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTTYPEID = CTT.CONTENTTYPEID AND CTT.TEMPLATE_ID = PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID AND CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTID = :"PSXSingleParam/sys_contentid" AND (PSX_TEMPLATE.AATYPE<>2 OR PSX_TEMPLATE.AATYPE IS NULL) ORDER BY PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME ASC

PSXDataSet.name: aadocactions_comm
PSXDataSet.description: This dataset generates actions for active assembly for documents. There will be one action per a variant with at least one slot registered. This variants considered are community dependent.

PSXDataSelector.nativeStatement: SELECT DISTINCT PSX_TEMPLATE.STYLESHEETNAME,PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID, PSX_TEMPLATE.ASSEMBLYURL, PSX_TEMPLATE.OUTPUTFORMAT, PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME FROM PSX_TEMPLATE, PSX_CONTENTTYPE_TEMPLATE, RXVARIANTSLOTTYPE, CONTENTSTATUS, RXVARIANTCOMMUNITY WHERE CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTTYPEID = PSX_CONTENTTYPE_TEMPLATE.CONTENTTYPEID AND PSX_CONTENTTYPE_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID = PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID AND PSX_TEMPLATE.TEMPLATE_ID = RXVARIANTCOMMUNITY.VARIANTID AND RXVARIANTCOMMUNITY.COMMUNITYID = :"PSXUserContext/User/SessionObject/sys_community" AND CONTENTSTATUS.CONTENTID = :"PSXSingleParam/sys_contentid" AND (PSX_TEMPLATE.AATYPE<>2 OR PSX_TEMPLATE.AATYPE IS NULL) ORDER BY PSX_TEMPLATE.NAME ASC

PSXDataSet.name: filterByContentType
PSXDataSet.description: This resource returns an XML document with content ids of items of supplied content type (sys_contenttypeid) filtered off of the supplied set of items (sys_contentid). Both parameters are required.

PSXDataSet.name: getWfStateIds
PSXDataSet.description: Retrieves workflow stateIds from ContentStatus for requested content ids.
